GUILTY of stealing goods, value 39s. -
Confined six months in the House of Correction ;
fined 1s.

Q. That was a private room? - A. Yes; there were only our three selves;
James Wooldridge
said to me, our foolish Frank has been taken up to Whitechapel-office for a bad Bank-note.

Q. Is there any body else here who saw him the first night? - A. Yes;
Ruth Morris
